    "119670254": {
      "title": "A result of existence for a model of two-phase flow in a porous medium made of different rock types",
      "abstract": "We consider a model describing two-phase immiscible and incompressible flows in a porous medium made of different rock types. This model leads to two coupled non-linear equations, the first one is elliptic and the other one is a degenerated equation of advection-diffusion, with nonlinear transmission conditions at the interface between different rock types. By mean of a mixed formulation, we obtain a result of existence and we give some results on the uniqueness."
    }
